casebody.data:
Thursday, January 4, 1996

RECONSIDERATION DOCKET

95-1703. Nehls v. Quad K. Advertising.

Cuyahoga County, No. 67358. Reported at 74 Ohio St.3d 1462, 656 N.E.2d 1298, and 74 Ohio St.3d 1485, 657 N.E.2d 1378. Nunc pro tunc, the announcement of December 20, 1995 is corrected to reflect the actual vote of the court: On motion for reconsideration. Motion granted and discretionary appeal allowed.

Resnick, F.E. Sweeney and Cook, JJ., dissent.
